\b monome grid
\b0 \
The top row is step enable/disable.\
\
The second row is the playback ruler.  Press a button in this row to jump loop playback from that point. A chorded two finger press will change loop length from first press to second press.\
\
remaining buttons\
vertical buttons = step\
horizontal buttons = scale degree\
\
use the arc (or mouse under the x/y positions under the data tab) to navigate around the grid. You'll notice the first and second row always display step enable/disable and the ruler, everything else moves 'underneath'\
