\b Encoder Recorder
\b0 \
If you have an arc4, you can use encoders 3 & 4 to function as a looping CV source. Make sure 'loop' is on, and the encoder output is enabled (with appropriate output destination, of course. To begin recording, tap the encoder button. plane will wait until the loop phase comes around (rec button blinks) and then start record (record button solid and playback button blinking) Playback begins with playback button is solid orange. \
\
